{"lemma":"شَمِلَ","slug":"شَمِلَ","root":"ش.م.ل","root_slug":"ش-م-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-م-ل","pos":"V","pos_camel":"verb","paradigm":[{"role":"past_2ms","form":"شَمِلْتَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_2fs","form":"شَمِلْتِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"past_2md","form":"شَمِلْتُما","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"past_2mp","form":"شَمِلْتُم","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_2fp","form":"شَمِلْتُنَّ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"past_3ms","form":"شَمِلَ","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_3fs","form":"شَمِلَت","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"past_3md","form":"شَمِلا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"past_3fd","form":"شَمِلَتا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"past_3mp","form":"شَمِلُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_3fp","form":"شَمِلْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2ms","form":"تَشْمَل","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2fs","form":"تَشْمَلِي","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2fs","form":"تَشْمَلِينَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2md","form":"تَشْمَلا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_2md","form":"تَشْمَلانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_2mp","form":"تَشْمَلُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2mp","form":"تَشْمَلُونَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2fp","form":"تَشْمَلْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3ms","form":"يَشْمَل","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3fs","form":"تَشْمَل","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3md","form":"يَشْمَلا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3md","form":"يَشْمَلانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3fd","form":"تَشْمَلا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3fd","form":"تَشْمَلانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3mp","form":"يَشْمَلُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3mp","form":"يَشْمَلُونَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3fp","form":"يَشْمَلْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"past_1mp","form":"شَمِلْنا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_1ms","form":"شَمِلْتُ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_1ms","form":"أَشْمَل","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_1mp","form":"نَشْمَل","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"}],"frequency_in_corpus":1,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":6,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23042","n23043","n23044","n23045","n23049","n23050"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%90%D9%84%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to contain, to encompass, to include, to enclose","examples":[{"text":"ماذا تَشمُلُ التَّوبَة، وكَيفَ تُساعِدُنا أن نُحارِبَ حالَتَنا كأشخاصٍ خُطاة؟","english":"What does repentance involve, and how does it help us combat our condition as sinners?"},{"text":"وتشمل هذه المصادر المهمة السِيَرَ الذاتية الإسلامية التقليدية لمحمد، والتي توفر معلومات إضافية عن حياته.","english":"These important sources include the traditional Islamic biographies of Muhammad, which provide additional information about his life."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make contain, to make include, to make enclose"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَمِلَ (šamila) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"little quantity left"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَمَلَ (šamala) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to expose to the north wind"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of شِمَال (šimāl)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"See the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23042","headword_ar":"شَمْلٌ","root":"$ml","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A state of union"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"composedness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a state of disunion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discomposedness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus having two contr. significations: (MF, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a united,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"composed, state of the affairs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the number,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) of a people, or company of men: (S, Msb, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a disunited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discomposed, state of the affairs"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.] thereof. (S, Mgh, Msb.) In imprecating evil upon enemies, (O, TA,) [or upon an enemy,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$at~ata A@ll~`hu $amolahumo","text_ar":"شَتَّتَ ا@للّٰهُ شَمْلَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"far~aqa A@ll~`hu $amolahumo","text_ar":"فَرَّقَ ا@للّٰهُ شَمْلَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fr~q All~`h $amolahu","text_ar":"فرّق اللّٰه شَمْلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God dissolve, break up, discompose, derange, disorganize, disorder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsettle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"united,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"composed, state of affairs;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$at~a $amoluhumo","text_ar":"شَتَّ شَمْلُهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May their united,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"composed, state of affairs"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"become dissolved, broken up, discomposed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (O, TA:) and [in the contr. case] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa A@ll~`hu $amolahumo","text_ar":"جَمَعَ ا@للّٰهُ شَمْلَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amolahu","text_ar":"شَمْلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God unite,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disunited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discomposed, state of affairs"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.]. (S, Mgh, Msb.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amalN","text_ar":"شَمَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: El-Ba'eeth says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"qado yanoEa$u A@ll~`hu AlfataY baEoda EavorapK\n                      \n                     \n                        waqado yajomaEu A@ll~`hu Al$~atiyta mina Al$~amalo"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sometimes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"often, God raises the young man after a stumble: and sometimes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"often, God unites,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"composes, what is dissolved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broken up, of the state of affairs"},{"kind":"text","text":"previously"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"united,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"composed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, O:) AZ cites this ex. in his “ Nawádir: ” (S:) but Aboo-'Omar El-Jarmee says that he had not heard the word thus except in this verse: (S, O:) Ibn-Buzurj, however, cites another verse as presenting an ex. of the same. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daxala fiY $amolihaA","text_ar":"دَخَلَ فِى شَمْلِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amalihaA","text_ar":"شَمَلِهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a he-camel that has become concealed among a herd of [she-] camels, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He entered amid their dense multitude:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) so in the M and the Moheet. (TA.)       -A2-  Also, (AHn, O, K,) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$imolN","text_ar":"شِمْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$imil~N","text_ar":"شِمِلٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A raceme of a palm-tree:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, O, K:) Et-Tirimmáh likens thereto a camel's tail: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as has little fruit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which some of the fruit has been plucked:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but AO used to say that it is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"produce"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spadix"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the male palm-tree, while not abundant and large."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaAlN","text_ar":"شَمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amolN mino junuwnK","text_ar":"شَمْلٌ مِنْ جُنُونٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fright, like insanity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amalN","text_ar":"شَمَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[used alone, and thus written]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["MF","TA","S","Msb","O","Mgh","K","AHn"]},{"entry_id":"n23043","headword_ar":"شِمْلٌ","root":"$ml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph, near the end."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n23044","headword_ar":"شَمَلٌ","root":"$ml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amolN","text_ar":"شَمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kanafN","text_ar":"كَنَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quarter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shelter"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protection"},{"kind":"text","text":"]:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkatifu","text_ar":"الكَتِفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the copies of the K being a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkanafu","text_ar":"الكَنَفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHonu fiY $amalikumo","text_ar":"نَحْنُ فِى شَمَلِكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY kanafikumo","text_ar":"فِى كَنَفِكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We are in your quarter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small quantity"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) of dates upon a palm-tree (S) or of ripe dates: (K:) and of rain: (S, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small number"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) of men and of camels (S) or of men &c.: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$omaAlN","text_ar":"اَشْمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and in like manner ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$umoluwlN","text_ar":"شُمْلُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. in all of these applications]; (K;) [or] as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a light quantity"},{"kind":"text","text":"of fruit of the palm-tree; (TA;) and the pl. of the latter is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaAliylu","text_ar":"شَمَالِيلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA","text_ar":"مَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY Aln~axolapi A_il~aA $amalN","text_ar":"عَلَى النَّخْلَةِ اـِلَّا شَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amalapN","text_ar":"شَمَلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaAliylu","text_ar":"شَمَالِيلُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not upon the palm-tree save a small quantity remaining of its fruit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAbaqiYa fiY Aln~axolapi A_il~aA $amalapN","text_ar":"مَابَقِىَ فِى النَّخْلَةِ اـِلَّا شَمَلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaAliylu","text_ar":"شَمَالِيلُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There remained not upon the palm-tree save somewhat in a sparse state"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of its fruit]: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSaAbanaA","text_ar":"اَصَابَنَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amalN mino maTarK","text_ar":"شَمَلٌ مِنْ مَطَرٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small quantity of rain fell upon us:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^ayotu $amalFA mina Aln~aAsi waAlA_ibili","text_ar":"رَاَيْتُ شَمَلًا مِنَ النَّاسِ وَالاـِبِلِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I saw a small number of men and of camels."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)       -A4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaAlN","text_ar":"شَمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places:       -A5-  And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amolN","text_ar":"شَمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence."}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n23045","headword_ar":"شَمِلٌ","root":"$ml","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wrapping,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inwrapping, himself"},{"kind":"text","text":"(↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$otamilN","text_ar":"مُشْتَمِلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amolap","text_ar":"شَمْلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (TA.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thin;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raqiyqN","text_ar":"رَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": thus expl. by Sh, as applied in this sense by Ibn-Mukbil to a she-camel's tail, which he terms"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liyf","text_ar":"لِيف"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n23049","headword_ar":"شَمَلٌّ","root":"$ml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaAlN","text_ar":"شَمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n23050","headword_ar":"شِمِلٌّ","root":"$ml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amolN","text_ar":"شَمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", near the end of the paragraph.       -A2-  Also, (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$imil~apN","text_ar":"شِمِلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K, TA;) the former applied to a he-camel; (TA;) and the latter to a she-camel, as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$imolaAlN","text_ar":"شِمْلَالٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$imoliylN","text_ar":"شِمْلِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K, TA,) which are likewise applied to a he-camel, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$imaAlN","text_ar":"شِمَالٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Light, active,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agile;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"swift."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K, TA.) Hence the phrase ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaA^oTaA^otu $imolaAliY","text_ar":"طَاْطَاْتُ شِمْلَالِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I hastened my light one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"my swift one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or, accord. to AA, he means his hand, or arm, called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$imaAl","text_ar":"شِمَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I lowered my left hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arm;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$imolaAlN","text_ar":"شِمْلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$imaAlN","text_ar":"شِمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning the same. (S, O.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","O","Msb","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}